sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Consumer
    participant API as Coordinator HTTPS
    participant R as Registry/Scheduler
    participant P as Provider
    participant GPU as Apple GPU

    C->>API: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(TLS + optional NaCl Box)
    API->>API: Auth, rate-limit, optional decrypt
    API->>API: Estimate tokens, reserve balance
    API->>R: ReserveProviderEx(model)
    R->>R: Apply routing gates + cost model
    R-->>API: Selected provider
    API->>API: Encrypt body to provider X25519 pub
    API->>P: inference_request (NaCl Box)
    P->>P: Decrypt with NodeKeyPair
    P->>GPU: Run MLX inference
    GPU-->>P: Generated tokens
    loop Streaming response
        P->>API: inference_chunk (NaCl Box to coord ephemeral)
        API->>API: Decrypt chunk
        API->>C: SSE data (TLS + optional re-seal)
    end
    P->>API: inference_complete + usage
    API->>API: Settle billing, refund/credit
